item.title: Appwrite Developer
item.description: Server github Contributing.md has details on Setting local dev setup. git clone https://github.com/appwrite/appwrite.git cd appwrite git submodule update --init docker compose build docker compose up -d Code Autocompletion docker run --rm --interactive --tty \ --volume $PWD:/app \ composer update --ignore-platform-reqs \ --optimize-autoloader --no-plugins --no-scripts --prefer-dist Then go to localhost
